Package com.atakmap.android.layers

Interface LayerScanner.Callback

  • Enclosing class:
    LayerScanner
    public static interface LayerScanner.Callback
    Interface that may be implemented to receive error, debugging, etc callbacks from this layer scanner. Instances of this interface should be provided to the layer scanner via the prepare() method.

      • getLayersDatabase

        LocalRasterDataStore getLayersDatabase()
        Returns the LocalRasterDataStore instance that the scanner will be populating. The scanner may use this reference to validate currency against the current catalog, mark layers as valid or delete layers when an update is required.
        Returns:
        The LocalRasterDataStore instance that the scanner is working to populate.
